channel.title: Anyone need a coder?
channel.description: Hello, i am looking for a server to code. I can code just about anything but only on 317. I have limits on 508+. If i code your server i will only be looking for about 45%+ of donation money. I have worked with top coders before. It doesnt matter if your server is mega popular or not.. i will be more than happy to code any server even if its got 5 players or 500 players. [b]Thankyou.[/b]
